🔥 Promoções da Semana

</h2>

<div class="produtos">

<div class="card">

<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/PlayStation_5_logo.svg">

<h3>PlayStation 5 Slim</h3>

<p class="preco-antigo">

R$ 4.799

</p>

<p class="preco">

R$ 2.999

</p>

<button>Comprar</button>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/95/Xbox_one_logo.svg">

<h3>Xbox Series X</h3>

<p class="preco-antigo">

R$ 4.499

</p>

<p class="preco">

R$ 2.799

</p>

